General.Name: SEP Acquisition Corp.
General.Description: SEP Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. The company intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or related business combination with one or more businesses. The company was formerly known as Mercury Ecommerce Acquisition Corp. and changed its name to SEP Acquisition Corp. in December 2022. SEP Acquisition Corp. was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Houston, Texas.
